  <brief_title>FloSeal Tubeless Exit Versus Cope Loop Nephrostomy Versus Fascial Stitch Following Percutaneous Nephrolithotripsy</brief_title>
  <official_title>Prospective Randomized Trial of Floseal Tubeless Exit vs. Cope Loop Nephrostomy vs. Fascial Stitch Following Percutaneous Nephrolithotripsy</official_title>
  <sponsors>
